"Release final safeties!
Final adjustments to positron accelerator cavity.
Firing in 9, 8, 7..."

"...What?!
High energy readings detected in the target!"
"The A.I.S. won't make it in time!"
"This isn't good! Ayanami's unit can't hold that back by itself!"

"Tracking Eva-01's shot...
Direct hit on the Angel confirmed!"
